snippet.title: Amber Heard Fired From Aquaman 2 Or Role Reduced? Rumors Say Maybe
snippet.description:
Amber Heard Fired From Aquaman 2 Or Role Reduced? Rumors Say Maybe

Rumors claim WB's considering firing Amber Heard from Aquaman 2 as Mera or reducing her screen time.

However, this report comes from We Got This Covered, so its veracity is dubious. Still, you never know. She's facing a pretty big backlash these days thanks to her drama with Johnny Depp.

I discuss in this video, so check it out.
